OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be mainly dry. Then remaining
OL,7,Fmostly dry and cloudy overnight
OL,8,Falthough some occasional rain possible
OL,9,Facross the Trossachs and western
OL,10,FTayside. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA cloudy day with rain at
OL,13,Ftimes across the west, mainly dry in
OL,14,Fthe east although patchy rain
OL,15,Fdeveloping here later. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
